invalid type: string "# UMA Health Report (v1.2.0)\n\n**Date**: 2026-05-08  \n**Status**: [OPERATIONAL - 100% HEALTH]  \n**Architecture**: Consolidated Three-Pillar Model  \n\n## 1. Structural Audit\n\nThe migration from the legacy 9-layer flat model to the **Three-Pillar Architecture** has been verified. All physical directories are correctly placed and restricted to their authorized domains.\n\n